### Test Chat API Endpoints

### Get conversations (requires authentication)
GET http://localhost:13000/chat/conversations
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Create a new conversation
POST http://localhost:13000/chat/conversations
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test Conversation",
  "participantIds": [2, 3]
}

### Get messages from a conversation
GET http://localhost:13000/chat/conversations/1/messages
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### Send a message
POST http://localhost:13000/chat/conversations/1/messages
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Hello, this is a test message!",
  "type": "TEXT"
}

### Get unread message count
GET http://localhost:13000/chat/messages/unread/count
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
